room_title: Escape room "Escape from Alcatraz" by Mind Games in Roseau
room_description:
Are you ready to be a prisoner of The Rock? Alcatraz was the most secure maximum security prison of its time holding the worst of the worst behind its bars. Step back in time to the 1940's when Al Capone and Bird Man would be your cellmates. It was believed that no one would ever escape.
You and your fellow inmates will need to work together to devise an escape or spend a lifetime locked behind bars. Welcome to the Rock.This will be electrifying.
